        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/17570412/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/17570412/" class="">第1页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/burce123/" class=" " title="在路上">在路上</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="17570412">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">Christer and Waller (1984a, b) developed a method for using subjective opinions of experts in estimation of the delay time distribution. This method was also used by Christer and Desa (1992) and Christer et al. (1994). For convenience, it is called the CW method.</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-03-31 21:10</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                Christer and Waller (1984a, b) developed a method for using subjective opinions of experts in estimation of the delay time distribution. This method was also used by Christer and Desa (1992) and Christer et al. (1994). For convenience, it is called the CW method.
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

